      "text": [
        "جَعَلَنَا اللهُ وَإِيَّاكُمْ مِمَّنْ يَسْعَى بِقَلْبِهِ إِلى مَنَازِلِ الاْبْرَارِ بِرَحْمَتِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "Allāh may, by His mercy, include us and you too among those who strive with their hearts for the abodes of the virtuous."
        ]
      }
    },
